summary:
Basement stables Whiterun and some extra storage outside Lakeview Manor
look at pics for more info.
descriptionHtml:
Whiterun stables in the first horse box there is a trapdoor.
In this basement you find more than 500.000 gold and other goods.
There are some hidden rooms and  a jail to keep some slaves or animals
included  Alchemy,  Enchanter and other usefull things to use or take. You have to search for the secret doors.

outside there are some extra storage barrels in different locations .
Lakeview manor,  and some other places have an URN to stash some things like KEYS or whatever ...... 

This is made with only the Skyrim ESM file.

Look at the pics
